dct_title_s: Municipal Civil Divisions Dane County, Wisconsin 2006
dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents municipal civil divisions for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2006. The dataset was originally published by the Dane County Land Information Office on February 14, 2007.[A county wide municipal boundaries dataset.]
